  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education as an opportunity for children with disabilities in Lokichar</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Vzdelanie ako &#x161;anca pre deti s postihnut&#xED;m v Lokichar</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">During the school year (July-September)volunteer will focus mainly to help with teaching children in classes (English, math, etc..) and tutoring disadvantaged children, on their arrival from school. During the holiday season (month of August) she will organize leisure activities for children (handicrafts, singing, games), focusing on their social and communication skills, HIV / AIDS prevention, familiarizing children and young people with life in Slovakia etc.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Po&#x10D;as &#x161;kolsk&#xE9;ho roka (mesiace j&#xFA;l a september) sa bude dobrovo&#x13E;n&#xED;k s&#xFA;stre&#x10F;ova&#x165; najm&#xE4; na pomoc s vyu&#x10D;ovan&#xED;m det&#xED; v triedach (angli&#x10D;tina, matematika a pod.) a na dou&#x10D;ovanie slab&#x161;&#xED;ch det&#xED; po ich pr&#xED;chode zo &#x161;koly. Po&#x10D;as pr&#xE1;zdnin (mesiac august) bude organizova&#x165; vo&#x13E;no&#x10D;asov&#xE9; aktivity pre deti (ru&#x10D;n&#xE9; pr&#xE1;ce, spev, hry), pri&#x10D;om sa zameria na ich soci&#xE1;lne a komunika&#x10D;n&#xE9; zru&#x10D;nosti, prevencia HIV/AIDS, obozn&#xE1;menie det&#xED; a mlad&#xFD;ch so &#x17E;ivotom na Slovensku, spolu bud&#xFA; h&#x13E;ada&#x165; aktivity a t&#xE9;my, ktor&#xE9; bud&#xFA; pre nich zauj&#xED;mav&#xE9;.</narrative>
  </description>
